===Glyph origin===
{{Han etym}}
{{Han compound|𣦼|食|ls=psc|c1=p|c2=s|t2=to eat; meal; food}}. Its original meaning was "to swallow".

===Etymology===
From {{inh|zh|sit-pro|*m-dz(j)a-k/n/t/s||to eat; food; to feed; rice}}, whence {{cog|bo|ཟ||to eat}}; probably also related to {{och-l|咀|to chew}} (STEDT; {{zh-ref|Benedict, 1972}}; {{zh-ref|Schuessler, 2007}}).

Alternatively, it may be compared to {{cog|bo|འཚལ||to eat}}, {{m|bo|ཚལ་མ||breakfast}} ({{zh-ref|Coblin, 1986}}; {{zh-ref|Schuessler, 2007}}; {{zh-ref|Hill, 2019}}).

